This is a basic project on Twitter Analysis. The three programs touch the introductory details of Social Network Analysis.
The twitter_acc file imported at the beginning is a python file which stores the 4 access credentials namely API key, secret API key, access token and secret access token.
A Developer account must be created at Twitter and on creatin an app via Twitter Developer Account, you can get these access credentials.
#####App_1######
This is the first program which allows users to stream live tweets based on certain keywords or stream tweets of a certain user.
#####App_2######
This program allows to create time series based on certain properties of tweets posted by a certain user. It also allows users to get relevant information about the tweets.
#####App_3######
This program touches the basic concept of Sentiment Analysis in Twitter using TextBlob and regex based on tweets posted by a certain user
